originalText.text: The best Dr. I’ve ever gone to.  Kind, caring, genuine, a dedicated professional.  A rare find in today’s world.  I was misdiagnosed with a serious illness , Dr. Cutler examined me and set me on the road to recovery in less than 24 hours.  He’s a brilliant Dr. and an honorable man.  He saved me from a surgery that would have kept me in pain the rest of my life.  30 years later I’m still grateful!!
